        <updateDate>2006-02-22T16:43:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Health Care COBRA OffSet Tax Savings Act of 2006 or the Health Care COSTS Act of 2006 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow certain individual taxpayers a refundable tax credit for 50% of the premium for COBRA continuation coverage under a group health plan. Requires notice of the availability of this tax credit to individuals entitled to COBRA continuation coverage.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
